# TACE CONTINUATION PROTOCOL

This conversation continues the development of the **TACE (Theory of Actualized Conscious Experience)** project. Please treat this as a continuation rather than a new discussion.

## Current Repository Status

The constitutional framework is established:

* TACE Philosophical Constitution (Canonical)
* TACE Semantic Constitution (Canonical)
* TACE Software Constitution (Canonical)

These constitutions are normative for the project. All future architectural decisions must remain consistent with them unless they are explicitly amended through the project's constitutional process.

