## ADR-003 Status

ADR-003 has been extensively refined and implemented.

Current architecture includes:

* Canonical Ask TACE pipeline
* Knowledge Realizer
* Canonical Expansion Package
* Recursive ontology retrieval
* Recursive expansion with cycle protection
* Immutable Canonical Expansion Package
* Canonical provenance
* Constitutional verification before AI assistance
* Rendering modes:

  * technical
  * academic
  * educational
  * popular
  * child
* Controlled AI Assistance
* AI acts only as a renderer, never as an ontology authority
* Longest-match canonical concept extraction
* Regression tests for canonical concept extraction
* Shared `QueryEngine.ask()` pipeline used by both terminal and web interface

The remaining architectural goal for ADR-003 is maintenance only.

