## Next Major Milestone

The next architectural task is:

**ADR-004 — Canonical Reasoning Engine**

Purpose:

Not:

> "What does the ontology say?"

but

> "What logically follows from the ontology?"

The Reasoning Engine should:

* perform formal logical inference
* derive canonical conclusions
* preserve provenance
* generate explicit proof chains
* never use statistical inference
* remain subordinate to the three constitutions and accepted ontology

Target architecture:

```
Ontology
        │
        ▼
Canonical Facts
        │
        ▼
Reasoning Engine
        │
        ▼
Derived Canonical Conclusions
        │
        ▼
Knowledge Realizer
        │
        ▼
Controlled AI Renderer
```

The AI remains only a renderer; all ontology retrieval and reasoning are performed by the canonical TACE components.

Please continue from this point without revisiting previously completed constitutional or ADR work unless required by a new architectural issue. Treat the constitutions and accepted ADRs as authoritative project documents rather than discussion drafts.

